@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Guitar Passion";
}

<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">My Guitar Journey</h1>
    <p class="lead">Welcome to my guitar hobby page! Here I share my passion for music and six strings.</p>
</div>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <img src="~/FE3491FE-4767-4FFB-B7FF-EFC924536A19.jpg" alt="Electric Guitar" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3" />
        <p>
            My journey with guitar started in college when I picked up an old acoustic from a friend. 
            What began as a casual interest quickly turned into a passionate hobby. I spend hours learning 
            new techniques, practicing scales, and trying to master my favorite songs.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <img src="~/PIC-7157.jpeg" alt="Acoustic Guitar" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3" />
        <p>
            I love exploring different music styles on guitar - from blues and rock to classical and jazz.
            Each style presents its own challenges and rewards. The guitar is such a versatile instrument
            that allows for endless exploration and creativity.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-4">
    <div class="col-12">
        <h2>Why I Love Guitar</h2>
        <p>
            Guitar has become more than just a hobby - it's a way to express myself and connect with others.
            There's something magical about creating music that can touch people's emotions. Whether I'm practicing
            alone in my room or jamming with friends, playing guitar brings me joy and peace.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you're interested in learning guitar too, I offer beginner lessons to share my passion for
            this amazing instrument. Check out my <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Calculator">lesson calculator</a>
            to see how affordable it can be to start your own guitar journey!
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
